{"title":"Windows11亚克力风格教程","uid":"c5f9a233be353bb47764a3a43a4b476b","slug":"Windows11亚克力风格教程","date":"2025-10-25T05:50:33.000Z","updated":"2025-10-25T05:59:17.609Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows11亚克力风格教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/icon.png","content":"<h1 id=\"让你的Windows变得更好看-亚克力玻璃风格\"><a href=\"#让你的Windows变得更好看-亚克力玻璃风格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"让你的Windows变得更好看(亚克力玻璃风格)\"></a>让你的Windows变得更好看(亚克力玻璃风格)</h1><p><em>注：此教程仅用 Windows 11 做演示</em></p>\n<p>部分效果预览：<br><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/AfterBeautify.png\" alt=\"Beautify\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>视频教程：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vhpxzqEAQ\">Bilibili</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"改变底部任务栏\"><a href=\"#改变底部任务栏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变底部任务栏\"></a>改变底部任务栏</h2><p>先下载这个软件：<a href=\"https://github.com/eUsEr114514/dataRepository/releases/download/1.0.0/windhawk_setup_offline.exe\">Windhawk</a> ←点击下载</p>\n<p>打开软件选择<strong>Explore</strong>一栏，下载图中框选的四个mods</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/WindhawkExplore.png\" alt=\"WindhawkExplore\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>下载这个：<a href=\"https://github.com/eUsEr114514/dataRepository/releases/download/1.0.0/W39.Code.walls.zip\">W39 Code &amp; walls</a> ←点击下载</p>\n<p>解压压缩包，打开<strong>Glass Taskbar.txt</strong>文件，复制整个文本<br>打开Windhawk的<strong>Taskbar Styler</strong> mod进入<strong>advanced</strong>设置<br>粘贴刚才复制的文本到<strong>Mod Settings</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/taskbarCode.png\" alt=\"TaskbarModSettings\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>点击<strong>Save</strong>保存后，你的任务栏就变的和这个一样啦<br>两边是透明的，中间为模糊玻璃风，圆角边界过渡</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/taskbarBeautify.png\" alt=\"TaskbarBeautify\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>当然如果你的任务栏变成了图标和状态栏重叠的样子（像这样）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/taskbarBug.png\" alt=\"TaskbarBug\"></p>\n<p>那就把复制的文本中的属性值改一下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot;CornerRadius=12&quot;,&quot;controlStyles[5].target&quot;:&quot;Grid#SystemTrayFrameGrid&quot;,&quot;controlStyles[5].styles[0]&quot;:&quot; *&quot;,&quot;controlSes[* 和 5].styles[1]&quot;:&quot;RenderTransform:=&lt;TranslateTransform X=\\&quot;-645\\&quot; Y=\\&quot;-2\\&quot;/&gt;&quot;,&quot;controlStyles[5].styles[2]&quot;:&quot;Padding=10&quot;,&quot;controlStyles[5].styles[3]&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>找到这段文本所在的位置↑<br>把其中的 <em>Margin&#x3D;0,7,-250,7</em> 和 <em>X&#x3D;&quot;-645&quot;</em> 里的数值改一下<br>我是改成 <em>Margin&#x3D;0,7,0,7</em> 和 <em>X&#x3D;&quot;-250&quot;</em> 的，你们可以参考一下</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"改变开始菜单栏\"><a href=\"#改变开始菜单栏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变开始菜单栏\"></a>改变开始菜单栏</h2><p>重新打开刚刚的<strong>W39 Code &amp; walls</strong>文件夹，找到里面的<strong>Glass Start Menu.txt</strong>文件，复制整个文本</p>\n<p>打开Windhawk的<strong>Start Meun Styler</strong> Mod进入<strong>Advanced</strong>设置<br>粘贴刚才复制的文本到<strong>Mod Settings</strong>里</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/MeunBeautify.png\" alt=\"MeunCode\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>点击<strong>Save</strong>保存后，你的开始菜单就变成了亚克力风格了，并且去除了下半部分</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/Meun.png\" alt=\"Meun\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"改变通知栏\"><a href=\"#改变通知栏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变通知栏\"></a>改变通知栏</h2><p>打开Windhawk的<strong>Notification Center Styler</strong> Mods进入Settings设置，展开<strong>Theme</strong>一栏，选择<strong>Translucentshell</strong>效果</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/NotificationCode.png\" alt=\"NotificationChoice\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>之后你的任务栏就变成了这样的亚克力风格</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/Notification.png\" alt=\"Notification\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"设置桌面小组件\"><a href=\"#设置桌面小组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置桌面小组件\"></a>设置桌面小组件</h2><p>下载这个：<a href=\"https://github.com/eUsEr114514/dataRepository/releases/download/1.0.0/UWidgets.zip\">UWidgets</a> ←点击下载</p>\n<p>解压后点击<strong>uWidgets.exe</strong>安装程序，随后打开软件</p>\n<p>进入<strong>Appearance</strong>，选中<strong>Font Family</strong>一栏<br>展开选择<strong>Microsoft YaHei</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/WidgetsAppearance.png\" alt=\"WidgetsAppearance\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>选中左边下面任意一栏，点击组件即可添加到桌面吗，随后可在桌面移动小组件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/WidgetsAdd.png\" alt=\"WidgetsAdd\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>进入<strong>Advanced</strong>栏，关闭<strong>Snap Position</strong>选项，打开<strong>Lock Position</strong>选项，这样子就能锁定住桌面小组件的位置了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/WidgetsAdvanced.png\" alt=\"WidgetsAdvanced\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>进入<strong>General</strong>栏，打开<strong>Run On Startup</strong>，这样子就能让UWidgets开机自启了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/WidgetsGeneral.png\" alt=\"WidgetsGeneral\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"改变资源管理器\"><a href=\"#改变资源管理器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变资源管理器\"></a>改变资源管理器</h2><p>下载这个：<a href=\"https://github.com/eUsEr114514/dataRepository/releases/download/1.0.0/ExplorerBlurMica.zip\">ExploreBlurMica</a> ←点击下载</p>\n<p>解压后找到<strong>register.cmd</strong>文件，用管理员身份运行</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/RunRegister.png\" alt=\"RunRegister\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>弹出成功的弹窗后，进入编辑<strong>config.ini</strong>文件<br>把这里的a值改小，我改成了140</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://electrondz75.top/linkImage/Picture/blog/WindowsBeautify/config.png\" alt=\"config\"></p>\n<hr>\n<details>\n    <summary>类MacOS任务栏</summary>\n    <p>Nexus下载链接：<a href=\"http://winstep.net/\" target=\"_blank\">http://winstep.net/</a></p>\n</details>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"完成！\"><a href=\"#完成！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完成！\"></a>完成！</h1>","feature":true,"text":"让你的Windows变得更好看(亚克力玻璃风格)注：此教程仅用 Windows 11 做演示 部分效果预览： 视频教程：Bilibili 改变底部任务栏先下载这...","permalink":"/post/Windows11亚克力风格教程","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84Windows%E5%8F%98%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%8B-%E4%BA%9A%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">让你的Windows变得更好看(亚克力玻璃风格)</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%BA%95%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E6%A0%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">改变底部任务栏</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95%E6%A0%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">改变开始菜单栏</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%A0%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">改变通知栏</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">设置桌面小组件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">改变资源管理器</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%EF%BC%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">完成！</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"电子","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://eUsEr114514.github.io/linkImage/Picture/headImage1v1.png","link":"/","description":"一个想出人头地的理想主义者CRY<br><a href=\"https://euser114514.github.io/homepage-main/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">个人主页</a>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/eUsEr114514","twitter":"https://twitter.com/ElectronDZ75","